{"sequence":74,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T12:57:26.767738848Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-1ed8576d","body":"`src/cli/milestone.rs:1881-1888` routes plan-inspection failures through `map_inspection_error`, and `src/cli/milestone.rs:2120-2127` wraps every non-milestone error into `MilestoneOperationFailed`. That includes the new `AppError::StaleMilestonePlan` raised by `validate_milestone_source_bundle_fresh` at `src/cli/milestone.rs:1992-1997`, so `milestone show/status` lose the structured staleness variant and callers can no longer match on the source run/bundle fields. The action path has the same issue via `ensure_execution_plan_available` at `src/cli/milestone.rs:1826-1833` and `map_action_error` at `src/cli/milestone.rs:2131-2138`. Pass `AppError::StaleMilestonePlan { .. }` through unchanged so downstream loads propagate structured staleness as required.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"0ec58c2ee99bbb0de2464d6de53d40c1bd640e7d262785c12063d7fcb4b53760","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260429063855","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":75,"timestamp":"2026-04-29T12:57:26.785704447Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-34dd104d","body":"The milestone controller resume path used from bead task execution can still bypass source-bundle freshness checks. `prepare_milestone_controller_for_execution` calls `resume_controller` directly at `src/cli/run.rs:1452-1459`, but the `ProjectMilestoneControllerRuntime::all_beads_closed` implementation at `src/cli/run.rs:1418-1433` only reads snapshot progress and never calls `validate_milestone_source_bundle_fresh`; the duplicate command runtime at `src/cli/milestone.rs:1712-1727` has the same blind spot. `resume_transition_request` then uses that result at `src/contexts/milestone_record/controller.rs:1035` and can transition Idle/Selecting controllers to Completed at `src/contexts/milestone_record/controller.rs:1052-1067` before any plan membership load triggers the new stale check. Add a source freshness validation before controller resume/completion decisions so a re-answered requirements bundle cannot leave the old materialized milestone silently marked complete or executable.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"d1cc47576075bc90c448ea9b5f33e4572e0fb23d853ac2fd9f6341c744fd0011","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260429063855","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
